bio:
Developer. I build things: Praise, Attest Fest, OP Citizen Attestation Explorer. 
Frens: Commons Stack, General Magic, Giveth, Token Engineering Commons
contributionDescription: I am part of the Praise team and also took the initiative to build Attest Fest for Optimism. In addition to the work I do within those projects (separate applications made) I try to contribute as best I can to advocate for Optimism in various forums .
